{"tid":921244,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"MAMAMOO突然現身聊天室...粉絲表現冷淡，回應「禁止聊天喔」","createTime":"2018-11-29T11:48:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T07:29:35.000Z","uid":74065,"like":60,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2698b823c90720549a3ad1ad3d1aec42b0ae3684","tid":921244,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T11:48:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3729/d3729449.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3729%2Fd3729449.jpg&h=0499ca0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲MAMAMOO突然現身聊天室，粉絲不相信，反應冷淡。（圖／翻攝自韓網）<br />\n<br />\n過去有許多偶像亂入「孤獨房」聊天群組，由時該群組有被規定「只能傳圖」，藝人若以文字打出真實身份，多半會被認為是詐騙，MAMAMOO也不例外，歌迷果然不相信她們就是本人。MAMAMOO於29日被貼出加入「孤獨房」的實況，4人貼出自拍照，主動打招呼：「你好，我們是MAMAMOO。」卻換來粉絲冷淡回應「禁止聊天喔」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3729/d3729452.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3729%2Fd3729452.jpg&h=4e88c21a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲MAMAMOO問歌迷「做什麼你們才會相信」。（圖／翻攝自韓網）<br />\n<br />\n歌迷根本不相信她們，MAMAMOO無奈傳了哭臉的表情符號，還傳訊息「相信我們」，下一句話，她們表示：「要怎樣做你們才會相信呢？」其中一名網友表示：「全部的人把手放到鼻孔裡。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3729/d3729448.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3729%2Fd3729448.jpg&h=c833ca91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲於是MAMAMOO就把手放到鼻孔裡了。（圖／翻攝自韓網）<br />\n沒想到，4個人真的照做，傳來一張她們把手指頭戳進鼻子的照片，正式認證她們就是本人，一系列的「孤獨房」聊天對話曝光，逗笑歌迷。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n笑到我"},{"pid":"1a5361eca5dca5bf4e98b99da711f18b4e3b1929","tid":921244,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T11:50:28.000Z","msg":"好想奶我條女華沙隻手指d鼻屎"},{"pid":"b1022ea83e264343957501bf7fb6d7a91e47a280","tid":921244,"uid":1408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T11:52:32.000Z","msg":"好鐘意睇明星亂入孤獨房<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65c19d692e477d81bb4ab59fe6c15246f6cc9768","tid":921244,"uid":18456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T11:54:36.000Z","msg":"頌樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"728ffad2ce6002360469874433fef0a563d410d3","tid":921244,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T12:18:15.000Z","msg":"叫佢地食埋鼻屎我先算係真"},{"pid":"80f8d6697477df168315e61cb42ad6e41d60589c","tid":921244,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T13:26:35.000Z","msg":"其實係啲fans想睇佢地啲鼻屎係點樣"},{"pid":"d2136493c047cfa67f80f451e21ff3056c187049","tid":921244,"uid":89660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T13:41:20.000Z","msg":"好正"},{"pid":"c2ce2d89e1330c8b80b043acbf986a77fd27da12","tid":921244,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2136493c047cfa67f80f451e21ff3056c187049","tid":921244,"uid":89660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T13:41:20.000Z","msg":"好正"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T13:43:11.000Z","msg":"收聲啦傻鳩"},{"pid":"bcff5e345b39cfa118d39b13c5753b3958d55f0c","tid":921244,"uid":89660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2ce2d89e1330c8b80b043acbf986a77fd27da12","tid":921244,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2136493c047cfa67f80f451e21ff3056c187049","tid":921244,"uid":89660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T13:41:20.000Z","msg":"好正"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T13:43:11.000Z","msg":"收聲啦傻鳩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T13:55:24.000Z","msg":"下= =&quot;"},{"pid":"8c33d289992d5fc